  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Breakfast Buffet </strong>is served from 7:00am – 10:30am. Enjoy the flavors of an authentic Sicilian breakfast with freshly prepared sweet pastries, local honey and jams, tasty cakes, cannoli, fresh yoghurt and fruit. Savory options such as omelets, panelle and arancine, cheeses and cold cuts, all accompanied by fresh bread. </p>
<p>Half Board and Full Board options are available for a supplement.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
