  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong><u>Restaurants &amp; Bars</u></strong></p>
<p>The restaurant and bar are close to the waterfront. In the warmer months breakfast, lunch and dinner can be enjoyed on the beachside terrace. There is also an indoor dining room for the cooler evenings. The a la carte restaurant serves traditional Sicilian cuisine</p>
<p>Light lunches and pizzas are also served by the pool.</p>
<p><strong><u>Pools &amp; Beaches</u></strong></p>
<p>The outdoor fresh water pool can be used during the summer months (Jun- Sep) and is open from 10:00am – 7:00pm.</p>
<p>The hotels private beach is a short stroll from the hotel. Walk through the dunes to the sandy beach and clear waters of Marina de Modica. A beach service is available from May – Sep and includes the use of the sun loungers (payable locally).</p>
<p><strong><u>Wellness Centre </u></strong></p>
<p>The Modica Beach Resort has a Wellness Centre that offers massages, facials and body treatments. It is equipped with a sauna and steam room. All wellness treatments and facilities are payable locally.</p>
<p><strong><u>General Facilities</u></strong></p>
<p>Free wifi</p>]]></facilityDescription>
