  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Executive Rooms </strong>are around 22-25m² and sleep up to two people in twin or double beds. A third bed can be added on request. The modern rooms are bright spacious and breezy, decorated in warm sandy tones crating a relaxing and comfortable environment. These rooms have a partial sea view. All rooms have a private bath or shower, air conditioning, television, minibar, safe and hairdryer.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Rooms </strong>are around 22-25m² and sleep up to two people. Decorated in the same fresh and modern style. These rooms offer see views with a small terrace.</p>
<p><strong>Family Rooms </strong>are available on request, please call to book.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
